high_descs: Walk to the stove on the right and look up at the cupboard.
Open the door on the right above the microwave, take out a plate, close the door.
Face the microwave above the stove.
Put the plate in the microwave, heat it up, take the plate out of the microwave, and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the sink on the left.
Place the plate inside of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a plate and put it in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the stove on the left of the counter, look at the cabinet above the microwave.
Take the plate out of the right cabinet above the microwave.
Bring the plate down from the cabinet.
Place the plate in the microwave, heat it up for a few seconds, take the plate back out.
Place the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the hot plate in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the microwave on your left.
Open the top middle-right cabinet and grab a plate from it.
Place the plate in the microwave, and remove it afterwards.
Place the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat a plate to put in the sink.
